property ancestor

on new me
  [  0] pushcons 0 .............................. <"objCharacter">
  [  2] pusharglist 1 ........................... <"objCharacter">
  [  4] extcall 34 .............................. <script("objCharacter")>
  [  6] pusharglist 1 ........................... <script("objCharacter")>
  [  8] extcall 0 ............................... <new(script("objCharacter"))>
  [ 10] setprop 33 .............................. ancestor = new(script("objCharacter"))
  [ 12] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 14] pushcons 1 .............................. <"modFader">
  [ 16] pusharglistnoret 2 ...................... <me, "modFader">
  [ 18] objcall 1717 ............................ me.addModule("modFader")
  [ 21] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 23] pushcons 2 .............................. <"modPositioning">
  [ 25] pusharglistnoret 2 ...................... <me, "modPositioning">
  [ 27] objcall 1717 ............................ me.addModule("modPositioning")
  [ 30] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 32] pushcons 3 .............................. <"modProp">
  [ 34] pusharglistnoret 2 ...................... <me, "modProp">
  [ 36] objcall 1717 ............................ me.addModule("modProp")
  [ 39] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 41] pushcons 4 .............................. <"modStretcher">
  [ 43] pusharglistnoret 2 ...................... <me, "modStretcher">
  [ 45] objcall 1717 ............................ me.addModule("modStretcher")
  [ 48] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 50] pushcons 5 .............................. <"modTeleport">
  [ 52] pusharglistnoret 2 ...................... <me, "modTeleport">
  [ 54] objcall 1717 ............................ me.addModule("modTeleport")
  [ 57] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 59] pushcons 6 .............................. <"modThespian">
  [ 61] pusharglistnoret 2 ...................... <me, "modThespian">
  [ 63] objcall 1717 ............................ me.addModule("modThespian")
  [ 66] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 68] pushcons 7 .............................. <"modWastedMode">
  [ 70] pusharglistnoret 2 ...................... <me, "modWastedMode">
  [ 72] objcall 1717 ............................ me.addModule("modWastedMode")
  [ 75] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 77] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <me>
  [ 79] extcall 35 .............................. return me
  [ 81] ret
end

on checkCollisions me, newLoc
  [  0] getparam 1 .............................. <newLoc>
  [  2] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <newLoc>
  [  4] extcall 35 .............................. return newLoc
  [  6] ret
end
